---
title: Herb-Butter Steak with Sweet Potato Fries and DIY Ranch Dressing Salad
description: Tonight's dinner is simple but delicious! We hope you enjoy this DIY ranch dressing as much as we do. It truly is the best topping for tender baby gem lettuce. Seared steak is topped with garlic and herbs and is served with oven-baked sweet potato fries. Enjoy!
